SUMMARY:Steve Flemming's Love Songs that Stir the Soul (Friday March 27th)
DESCRIPTION:Try New Things in Toronto!\nHello everyone\,\n\nPlease join us
  **on zoom** for a fun\, relaxing and inspiring evening with **Love Songs 
 that Stir the Soul.**\n\nSongs that I have written for well over 36 years.
 \nYou will love what you hear! :)\nNew songs every week\, including some o
 f our favorites!\n\n\\*You are welcome to join us any time after 8:30 pm (
 Eastern Time)\n\\*You are also welcome to come on later in the evening as 
 well\n**\\*\\*Attend for free if you like - if it's your first time attend
 ing :)**\n\nEvent Details below:\n\nSincerely\,\n\nSteve Flemming\n(Songwr
 iter/Producer/Host)\n\nEvent Details:\n**Steve Flemming's Love Songs that 
 Stir the Soul (Friday\, March 27th)**\n**(on Zoom)**\n\n\\*Original Lyrics
  and Songs by Songwriter and Producer Steve Flemming\n\n\\*Story songs\, l
 ove songs\, spiritual songs\, songs about nature\, our culture\, our past\
 , our future\, relationships and our lives\n\nI'll be playing a mix of son
 gs using a fusion of mixed genres like\, **Folk\, Traditional Folk\, Count
 ry\, Blue Grass\, Singer Song Writer\, Soft Rock\, Easy Listening\, Classi
 c Rock\, R & B\, Gospel\, Pop\, Adult Contemporary\, Indie Rock/Po**p and 
 many others genres too. So please sit back and get ready to have an amazin
 g auditory experience in the comforts of your own home :)\n\n\\*You can co
 me on and off at any time during the night- starting at 8:30 pm\n\n**About
  Steve Flemming:**\nHighly influenced by the great singer songwriters of t
 he 50s\, 60s\, 70s\, 80s and 90s. I have been writing my own songs since 1
 990. Songs about life\, love\, loss\, hope\, faith\, joy\, romance\, memor
 ies\, spirituality and heartbreak. Songs that are universal\, heartfelt an
 d often relevant to the lives of many others.\n\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\
 n**Event Fee:**\n\n**Pay What You Can: (P.W.Y.C)**\nYou can kindly send th
 rough e transfer or pay pal to:\n**steveflemming11@gmail.com**\n\n-Anythin
 g you can contribute is greatly appreciated to help support this meaningfu
 l musical endeavor and song loving community\n\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\
 -\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n**Zoom link:**\n\nhttps
 ://us04web.zoom.us/j/495043928\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-
 \\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n\n**Testimonials from Past Events:**\nYour songs
  are wonder-full\, speak to emotions\, experiences and moments we've all f
 elt and lived. S. B.\nSteve Flemming is an amazing songwriter whose lyrics
  stir the soul. He transforms everyday thoughts and life into beautiful po
 etry and magical tunes. Amazing stuff yet again Steve. - L.L.\nSteve\, tha
 nk you for a night of heartfelt\, exhilarating\, and inspiring music.\nV.R
 .\nThanks for having me my friend. I love your words\, they calm me and en
 ergize me at the same time I'll look forward to your next invite\nM.Z.\nTh
 ese great songs definitely helped me to decompress after a long day. Keep 
 up the song writing Steve\, these are great! - S.S.\nThank you so much for
  a relaxing evening and sharing your inspiring music Steve! I am excited t
 o hear more and I hope you do this again!! - C.B\nLovely songs and a great
  vibe with wonderful people. I couldn’t have asked for a better way to c
 lose my day. Huge thanks Steve\, for inviting me! I truly enjoyed every mo
 ment! - N.A.\nThe lyrics are amazing. From the heart...\nThanks Steve for 
 the amazing tunes. I'm truly blown away. Very glad I joined.\n\\- E\\.E\\.
 \n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-
